A \subseteq C\,
\,B \subseteq D,\,
\,A \times B \subseteq C \times D.
B\subseteq D\iff b \in B \rightarrow  b \in D
A \times B = \{(a, b)\mid a\in A, b\in B\}
A\times B \subseteq C \times D \;\;\text{ if and only if}\;\;\; (a, b) \in A\times B \rightarrow (a, b) \in C \times D
